      "text": "Last edit almost 3 years ago by svayambhu108\n84\nNeeds Review\n84\n80 So that's what Ubik is: the mind - actually the true present - of which the world is in its ossified forgotten memory contents (which appear to be in the present but are really in the past - exactly as put forth in \"Ubik\"! the contents regress but the mind - Ubik - doe not. + Ubik is the Paraclete + Logos both. It has traveled down into this ossified complex (in the Jungian sense) to dissolve it! It has made a microform \"phagocyt",
